# Tests from php-src/ext/json/tests/ intentionally NOT rewritten for the
# fastjson compat harness. Format: <basename>.phpt # <category> # reason
#
# Categories:
#   ext-json-internals : exercises ext/json-only behavior fastjson does
#                        not currently aim to mirror byte-for-byte.
#   doc-divergence     : asserts a behavior fastjson explicitly diverges
#                        from, with a one-line reason inline.
#   bug-report         : tracks a fastjson bug; remove once fixed.
#
# Re-run with:
#   scripts/sync-upstream-json-tests.sh && \
#   php run-tests.php tests/upstream-json/

